Privacy policy
Thank you for using Cold Shower! This privacy policy explains how we handle your personal information or data while
    using our app.
Information Collection and Use
Cold Shower does not collect any personal information from its users. We do not require you to provide any personal data
such as your name, email address, or phone number. We also do not store any user data on our servers.
Information Sharing
We do not share any personal information or data collected from our users with third parties, except for the following
cases:
The Cold Shower app may contain links to third party websites. By clicking on these links, you will be redirected to
    the respective third party website. Please note that once you leave our app and enter a third party website, our
    privacy policy no longer applies. We recommend reviewing the privacy policies of any third party websites you visit.
Your privacy is important to us, and we are committed to keeping your information secure.
Data Security
We take the security of your information seriously. We have implemented appropriate measures to protect your data from
unauthorized access or disclosure. Please note that while we do not track any user data, Google may track app
installations and other statistics.
Changes to this Policy
We reserve the right to update or change this privacy policy at any time. Any changes will be posted on this page.
Acceptance of this policy
By continuing to use Cold Shower, you acknowledge and accept the terms and conditions outlined in this privacy policy.
If you do not agree with this policy, please refrain from using the app. Your continued use of the app after any
modifications to this policy will signify your acceptance of the updated terms.
Contact Us
If you have any questions or concerns about our privacy policy, please contact us at bitsofadventures@gmail.com.